GET http://localhost:5001/health/live

### Readiness — checks critical dependencies
GET http://localhost:5001/health/ready


### Create a payment - happy path
POST http://localhost:5001/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "merchant_acme",
  "idempotencyKey": "key-021",
  "amount": 49.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "customerEmail": "[email protected]",
  "method": "CreditCard",
  "metadata": null
}
